    CBOR integer (major type = 0 or 1).

    CBORTagProcessor
    The interface for tag processors.
    CBORToken<TValue>
    CBOR token that the CBOR tokenizer (CBORTokenizer) constructs.
    CBORTokenizer
    A tokenizer that tokenizes the content of an input stream of CBOR data items so that the CBOR decoder (CBORDecoder) can construct CBOR data items (CBORItem).
    CBORTooLongException
    The exception raised when the length or the size of a CBOR data item is too long.
    CBORUndefined

    CBORUri

    CBORValue<TValue>

    CPBignum
    A tag processor for the tag number 2 and the tag number 3, which represent an unsigned bignum and a negative bignum, respectively.
    CPDefault
    A tag processor that returns a CBORTaggedItem instance that has the tag number and the tag content passed as arguments of the process method.
    CPUntag
    A tag processor that just removes the tag.
    CPUri
    A tag processor for the tag number 32, which indicates that the following text string is a URI.
